Package: kzsh
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libstdc++6, libncurses6, libreadline8
Description: Kuznix Shell - a bash-like shell
 Kuznix Shell (kzsh) is a modern, bash-compatible shell written in C/C++ with
 support for builtins, history, aliases, and configuration through rc files.
 It provides an interactive command line and supports scripting.

Package: kzsh-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: kzsh (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Development files for Kuznix Shell
 Development headers and libraries for building software that links against
 Kuznix Shell. This package contains header files and static libraries used
 by developers integrating with kzsh.
